task.summary: Added support for mac. Changed buffer from LIFO to FIFO Found problems with the module loader...
Small fixes. Changed the plugins and config directory to static directories on the system. Added build rules for application and plugins. Added ability to build true Mac apps.
Small changes. Untested experimental change in the handeling of preferences.
Small fixes and restructuring. Tested the new preference handling.
Added a new menu bar icon. Added automatic detection of USB devices. Added more Ambilight modes.
Stability improvements. Better color correction and stepping.
Fixed color smoothening not reaching zero.
Large update in the color fetcher.
Fixed hanging problem in the LightHandler. Updated algorithm for taking average of pixel before post processing.
